      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty \u2013 it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car from day one, and it's in pristine condition inside and out. No scratches, no spills, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner because it still has that brand-new feel! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
