      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in flawless shape\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and the paint is literally sparkling. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how perfect it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
