    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E36 M3, featuring the high-revving S50B30 inline-six engine with variable valve timing (VANOS) in peak operational status. This example boasts exceptional mechanical sympathy, evidenced by its consistent compression across all cylinders and a leak-down test result of under 3%. The drivetrain is anchored by a ZF 5-speed manual gearbox with a refreshed shift linkage, delivering torque to a factory 3.15 limited-slip differential. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, with the subframe mounting points inspected and found to be in showroom condition. Performance is further enhanced by a Bilstein/Eibach suspension geometry, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup provide maximum lateral grip and communicative feedback. The paint depth is uniform across all panels, and the forged Style 24 wheels are free of any curb rash, maintaining original factory specifications throughout.",
